&lt;div class=&quot;tl-millions-row&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;tl-date&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;tl-stories&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;tl-desc&quot;&gt;Billions of years pass, far more time than has been accounted for up till now.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
